Program: Outlook
Title: The Best of Outlook 2013 - Part One
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p01n9gtq
Last Broadcast Date: Boxing Day 2013
Another chance to hear some of our most inspiring and popular stories from 2013 including: Afghanistan's first woman military helicopter pilot on taking to the air with her baby daughter; the real life woman behind the painting known as The Green Lady; the teenage garment worker rescued from under the rubble of collapsed Rana Plaza factory in Bangladesh; the Italian diver who cuddles sharks and the Syrian film buff keeping his historic cinema open at all costs. Show less